text: Filippos Karvelas was a gymnast from Greece. Filippos competed at the 1896 Summer Olympics. He was born in 1877 and died on 7 November 1952.Filippos Karvelas == References == Category:1877 births Category:1952 deaths Category:Greek gymnasts Category:Olympic bronze medalists for Greece Category:Sportspeople from Athens
